-- Johannesburg's Stock Exchange Says Starts Index to Measure Rand Volatility
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-01T08:11:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/johannesburg-s-stock-exchange-says-starts-index-to-measure-rand-volatility.html
Johannesburg’s stock exchange started
the Rand Index, which will be used to calculate the value of
South Africa’s currency against a basket of currencies, JSE Ltd.
said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
